OL,3,CMovie about Cimarons released across
OL,4,CUK in Black History Month celebrations
OL,6,FA documentary by two North East
OL,7,Ffilmmakers is appearing in cinemas
OL,8,Facross the country including at the
OL,9,FTyneside Cinema.
OL,11,F'Harder than a Rock' tells the story
OL,12,Fof Britain's first reggae band, The
OL,13,FCimarons, and is being shown as part
OL,14,Fof Black History Month.
OL,16,FIt is from the North East-based
OL,17,Fproduction companies Margot Films and
OL,18,FJ6 Films, which worked with the
OL,19,Fcinematographer Mark Warmington.
