OL,6,FThe film's release follows its world
OL,7,Fpremiere earlier this year at the
OL,8,FSheffield DocFest where it received a
OL,9,Fstanding ovation from the crowd.
OL,11,FThe Cimarons were created by a group
OL,12,Fof teenage Jamaican immigrants in
OL,13,FLondon in 1967, and were at the
OL,14,Fforefront of the reggae explosion in
OL,15,FBritain in the 1970s.
OL,17,FThroughout their career the group
OL,18,Fcollaborated with the likes of Bob
OL,19,FMarley, Jimmy Cliff, and Sir Paul
OL,20,FMcCartney.
