OL,6,FDespite this, according to the
OL,7,Ffilmmaker, the Cimarons have been
OL,8,Flargely under-recognised.
OL,10,FSpeaking to ITV News Tyne Tees, Mark
OL,11,FWarmington said the film being made
OL,12,Fwas a 'happy accident.'
OL,14,F"I was introduced to a guitar player
OL,15,Fcalled Locksley Gichie about four and
OL,16,Fa half years ago who was the guitarist
OL,17,Fin the Cimarons who told me all these
OL,18,Famazing stories about the band's
OL,19,Fhistory, what they'd done, and I
OL,20,Fcouldn't believe I'd never heard of
OL,21,Fthem.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/5
