OL,6,F"They're massively under-recognised.
OL,7,FTheir importance in not just reggae
OL,8,Fbut British music culture,. They're a
OL,9,Freally important band and most people
OL,10,Fhave never heard of them. I guess
OL,11,Fthat's why I wanted to make the film,
OL,12,Fto right that wrong of that
OL,13,Frecognition."
OL,15,FMichael Arkk from the band added that
OL,16,Fmaking the film was 'fun' and said:
OL,17,F"It was my first time doing a thing
OL,18,Flike this so I had a great time."
